{"tid":324601,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"龜頭Bob笠頭持鎅刀周街走","createTime":"2017-07-16T14:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T14:39:43.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce28b17f5bc79b9fab1f4fac7600906171bc75c1","tid":324601,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/221620_c24521ac091af25a136c9d46e8ebc57c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F221620_c24521ac091af25a136c9d46e8ebc57c.jpg&h=badc9f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林盛斌（Bob）昨日為電影《西謊極落：太爆．太子．太空艙》到筲箕灣街頭拍攝宣傳片，他笠頭、手持鎅刀扮大賊，但搞笑多過驚嚇，被途人無視。他又到餐廳與食客玩自拍，𧨾得大家好開心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uxfnb8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uxfnb8&d=lkS6DTQKXjoRIIxnjKOnfQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8a428e7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uxfnb8</a>"},{"pid":"efeb4652acd7888fea7fe9174e16f14b97178d49","tid":324601,"uid":29724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083457e3b1f74c4ba603c26ef1902c8dced0e3d8","tid":324601,"uid":37600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:39:43.000Z","msg":"睇個名都知係垃圾戲"}]}